sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant FE as Frontend
    participant API as FastAPI
    participant W as Job Worker
    participant NB as nano banana
    participant TTS as edge-tts
    participant TH as SadTalker/Wav2Lip
    participant FF as FFmpeg

    U->>FE: selfie + persona description
    FE->>API: POST /api/avatars
    API->>W: avatar_styling job
    W->>NB: style(selfie, persona, identity-pinned)
    NB-->>W: portrait.png
    W-->>FE: awaiting_approval
    U->>FE: Approve (or Regenerate)
    U->>FE: voice + Generate
    FE->>API: POST /video {mode:a, voice, avatar_id}
    API->>W: render_mode_a job
    W->>TTS: speak(script, voice)
    TTS-->>W: mp3 + word timings
    W->>TH: render(portrait, wav)
    TH-->>W: talking-head mp4
    W->>FF: pad/scale + burn subtitles + loudnorm
    FF-->>W: output.mp4
    W-->>FE: done → player + download
